title: S7E23 – "Feed Your Fears" – Scary Stories Told in the Dark
description:
In this episode of Scary Stories Told in the Dark, we bring you five spine-chilling tales from author James Colton, performed by host and narrator Otis Jiry, about dental disasters, paranormal punishments, sinister senses, homewrecking hauntings, and vengeful vegetation.
